import './db'
import './public/models/Webtoon'
import app from './app'

const PORT = 5050

const handleListening = () =>
  console.log(`✅ Server listenting on http://localhost:${PORT}`)

app.listen(PORT, handleListening)

import mongoose from 'mongoose'

mongoose.connect('mongodb://127.0.0.1:27017/wbank')

const db = mongoose.connection

const handleOpen = () => console.log('✅ Connected to DB ')
const handleError = (error) => console.log('❌ DB Error', error)

db.on('error', handleError)
db.once('open', handleOpen)

// @ts-check

import express from 'express'
import { joinMembership, login } from '../controllers/userController'
import { home, search } from '../controllers/toonController'
const mainRouter = express.Router()

mainRouter.get('/', home)
mainRouter.get('/join', joinMembership)
mainRouter.get('/login', login)
mainRouter.get('/search', search)

export default mainRouter

import express from 'express'
import {
  edit,
  remove,
  login,
  logout,
  joinMembership,
} from '../controllers/userController'

const userRouter = express.Router()

userRouter.get('/login', login)
userRouter.get('/joinMembership', joinMembership)
userRouter.get('/logout', logout)
userRouter.get('/edit', edit)
userRouter.get('/remove', remove)
userRouter.get('/:id', login)

export default userRouter

import express from 'express'
import { thumbnailUpload } from '../../middlewares'
import {
  info,
  getUpload,
  postUpload,
  getEdit,
  postEdit,
  deleteToon,
} from '../controllers/toonController'

const toonRouter = express.Router()

toonRouter.get('/:id([0-9a-f]{24})', info)
toonRouter
  .route('/upload')
  .get(getUpload)
  .post(thumbnailUpload.single('thumbnail'), postUpload)
toonRouter
  .route('/:id([0-9a-f]{24})/edit')
  .get(getEdit)
  .post(thumbnailUpload.single('thumbnail'), postEdit)
toonRouter.route('/:id([0-9a-f]{24})/delete').get(deleteToon)

export default toonRouter

/** \\d+ = 숫자만 받음 */
